{"tid":1536682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"831速龍闖太子站無差別攻擊 四格多鏡頭同步片段","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T23:45:29.000Z","uid":206090,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1b948e19bcc35f42d1910716316dc0642774c530","tid":1536682,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"幾條直播片同網上片段同步處理，同一刻發生的多鏡頭視角。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">用1080p睇最清。</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l97TM_O3D-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl97TM_O3D-g&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=578f25b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l97TM_O3D-g</a>"},{"pid":"a03e5461d87aa69c66f67309c37966e74e2f1849","tid":1536682,"uid":88768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">太子殺人犯</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1669 鍾國恩 警長<br />\n48958 李彼得 高級警員<br />\n54538 張文麟 高級警員<br />\n58248 梁智顯 高級警員 <br />\n52080 張達雄 高級警員<br />\n再加 8692 (未confirm)<br />\n<br />\n一定要推阿！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n推！！太子有片 六個殺人犯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9a9650d57a8485ad61c21622e8d749a66e47d382","tid":1536682,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:54:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"620d57fe446279f37c42f8798b49c93fb463739e","tid":1536682,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:00:20.000Z","msg":"如果太子站真係有人死咗<br />\n你哋會點做？<br />\n只係不斷屌鳩黑警？<br />\n黑警係唔會痛佢哋一早失去人性<br />\n你哋會唔會攞起武器<br />\n向殺人兇手討回公道？<br />\n就算係見到速龍衝過嚟<br />\n好多時都係冇人會敢去抵抗<br />\n全部走哂<br />\n走唔到就落單被人捉<br />\n捉完嘅被狗打被狗搞<br />\n你哋仲想見到幾多個手足48之後被人打到殘廢？<br />\n有幾多女手足被人老強？"},{"pid":"4ed7de3a84b751b5696400df8bc092bba1afd822","tid":1536682,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:06:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"502fa5e1bc38b818132642afb2bdd454bbe18a7f","tid":1536682,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2c8abb0ab36b2d106b1d20fadebcdc51d239457","tid":1536682,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家快啲打國際輿論線呀！！！<br />\n最近好多核彈！！！<br />\n<br />\n1. 侵侵叫中共還清朝債券&rarr;香港回歸合法性問題<br />\n2. 白衫男以言入罪無辜被黑警打&rarr;香港失去言論自由、警權過大<br />\n3. 太子站黑警濫暴打傷無辜市民 黨鐵拒交CCTV包庇&rarr;警權過大、官商勾結<br />\n4. 太子站黑警拒絕救傷員入內救援傷者&rarr;人道危機<br />\n5. 林鄭錄音流出指特首無權辭職 無能力處理政治問題&rarr;一國兩制已死<br />\n<br />\n全部同我推爆佢呀！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1a85e89413537cf00da031510ced4c8144b5a3ec","tid":1536682,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T22:30:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b7392d264a0d4d269483e5788a9527cc5b2c4d2","tid":1536682,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T22:31:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee9967ed421304a9bf41241ae201d9393ecf13b7","tid":1536682,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T00:46:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e159251d2affc710a4f6a131e35b38a2f017b93","tid":1536682,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"[律師建議］ 緊急 請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n831太子站當日有份俾人打嘅市民，請盡快聯絡律師做民事訴訟(personal injuries)，向法庭申請要地鐵攞CCTV。<br />\n<br />\n一定要快，如果過咗期限，地鐵話自動洗咗啲CCTV，到時就真係冇人知道太子發生過咩事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n註：其實唔止身體受傷，心靈受創都可以告。當日喺現場目擊事件，造成精神痛苦，都可以嘗試用 secondary victim （非直接受害人）去追討。最後告唔告得入唔係最重要，目的係令多啲人有權拎CCTV，還原真相⚠️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟 98190979<br />\n民陣 65499452<br />\n民權觀察 94632945<br />\n伍展邦律師行 26081400<br />\n<br />\n推呀！！唔想有人抄車，但更加唔想抄左車但冇人知！！黑警一定要還債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追究到底！"},{"pid":"86a598cc78224759636c65b1bb882dda809fd631","tid":1536682,"uid":53840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435ff8c90d8f09762ec966280754c4305bc6ca41","tid":1536682,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45a24844ab943bc87d8e945441fbae6ff714f64e","tid":1536682,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"準備"},{"pid":"f71e1b9e7f16c7958e182ca180ab084efc9b2a31","tid":1536682,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:41:10.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537277</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 註冊Twitter 帳號。<br />\n2. 找到要post 上Twitter 的影片。<br />\n3. 複制facebook影片連結貼上到以下網頁 (需要登入及縛定Twitter 帳戶， facebook影片分享必需是公開)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://transferring-videos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferring-videos.com&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=f0d00459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transferring-videos.com</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7bac7b0314f462edfa0757580f5b756017e125","tid":1536682,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7440bb4a10ab5a3a5010d5ef4e7a3c6c297a98f2","tid":1536682,"uid":69719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8980526a7f429292477669f433d6c3e320a63c44","tid":1536682,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"已post上twitter, 大家都請幫手 upload 片"},{"pid":"66358d40029554501c40ac5929419d9627354e2c","tid":1536682,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871c77dca712a98f86173bca0527070e2b54fe66","tid":1536682,"uid":114291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"一定要推！"},{"pid":"9745ad9d78f69e572ee5f89863038b3f656a5182","tid":1536682,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"（多台）全民皆兵，義教防身方法及體能訓練正式上線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537624</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a7435e731efa0e13ae7161e5cd390c03e823e3c","tid":1536682,"uid":13343,"like